<BR>
In plain terms. Yes, the spear drops from the bears in the pits, but from a different named bear that is a extremly rare pop and as far as i know dont have any special placeholder (that is, if you cant wipe em all dont even think about it).<BR>
<BR>
from extensive hunting down there i would say this bear turn up about once in every 30-40 or so wipeouts of all the mobs down there. And thats higly calculated.<BR>
<BR>
The nice thing about the spear is however that it does indeed fit in the range slot.</font></td></tr></table>
